## Loading R packages

In the code chunk below, [`p_load()`] of pacman pkg is used to load tidyverse family of packages.

```{r}
pacman::p_load(tidyverse)
```

```{r}
realis <- read_csv("data/realis2019.csv")
```
```{r}
ggplot(data = realis, aes(x = `Unit Price ($ psm)`)) + geom_histogram()

```
